Welcome to MusicBoard!

------------------------------------|

> Install MusicBoard

Go To the "MusicBoard_1_4" Folder (more info there) and enter it in Terminal to Install Deb:

dpkg -i musicboard

(or with GDebi)

Execute in any Terminal:

musicboard

-------------------------------------|

For Help go to " Help.txt " or to the Help panel in MusicBoard.

For Q&A go to " Q&A.txt " (to ask a question, go to: musicboardcontact@protonmail.com ).

For To Do go to " To_Do " .

For About go to the About panel in MusicBoard.

For the Licence go to " Licence.txt " or to the Licence panel (found in Help).

For Documentation go to " Documentation.pdf " .

Dev. Details:

- The Rec. module is made by Qt: http://doc.qt.io/archives/qt-5.5/qtmultimedia-audiorecorder-example.html
- Sounds found at: www.musicradar.com (Free)   
- Libraries: QFont, audiorecorder.h, ui_audiorecorder.h,  QApplication, QShortcut,  QtWidgets, QAudioProbe, QAudioRecorder, QDir, 
QFileDialog and QMediaRecorder.

